The paper deals with a problem of allocating resources to customers over time, which involves both online learning and optimization. The use of online learning suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning), while the optimization aspect could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The problem of allocating resources to customers can also be viewed as a game-theoretic problem, which could make it relevant to cs.GT (Game Theory). Finally, the use of inventory balancing techniques could suggest a connection to cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
